<view class="container about-page">
  <view class="card about-hero">
    <view class="section-title">关于我们</view>
    <view class="about-sub">这里集中说明这款工具能帮你解决什么问题、适合哪些人使用，以及遇到问题时怎么联系和处理。</view>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">协议与隐私</view>
    <view class="about-copy">在使用登录、头像、资料保存等功能前，我们会先说明收集信息的目的、方式和用途，并在你明确同意后才开始处理相关信息。</view>
    <view class="about-field-card">
      <view class="about-label">当前授权状态</view>
      <view class="about-static-value">{{privacyConsentAgreed ? '已同意《用户服务协议》和《隐私政策》' : '未同意，系统不会采集登录、头像和档案信息'}}</view>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="openServiceAgreement">先看服务说明</button>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="openPrivacyPolicy">再看隐私说明</button>
      <button class="primary-btn about-ghost-btn" wx:if="{{!privacyConsentAgreed}}" bindtap="agreePolicies">确认我已阅读</button>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">这款工具想帮你什么</view>
    <block wx:for="{{positioning}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="about-item">
        <view class="about-item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="about-copy about-item-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">适用人群</view>
    <view class="about-grid">
      <block wx:for="{{audiences}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="about-mode about-mode-light">
          <view class="about-item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="about-copy about-mode-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">你能直接感受到的特点</view>
    <view class="about-copy">我们更重视结果能不能看懂、能不能拿去和家长讨论、能不能直接辅助排表，而不是只给一个难理解的结论。</view>
    <block wx:for="{{differentiators}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="about-item">
        <view class="row-between about-item-top">
          <view class="about-item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="about-badge">{{item.badge}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="about-copy about-item-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">你会怎么使用它</view>
    <view class="about-copy">不是一上来就看复杂分析，而是先查基础数据，再看 5 层推荐，最后按需要补充深度分析。</view>
    <view class="about-grid">
      <block wx:for="{{aiExperienceModes}}" wx:key="title">
        <view class="about-mode about-mode-{{item.tone}}">
          <view class="about-item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="about-copy about-mode-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
        </view>
      </block>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">小程序怎么用最省时间</view>
    <view class="about-copy">如果你是第一次使用，建议按下面这个顺序走，最容易看懂，也最适合和家长一起讨论。</view>
    <block wx:for="{{usageGuide}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="about-item">
        <view class="about-item-title">{{index + 1}}. {{item.title}}</view>
        <view class="about-copy about-item-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">研发与技术背景</view>
    <view class="about-copy">我们更重视数据链路、推荐解释和高峰期可用性，目标不是把话说复杂，而是把结果做扎实、做清楚。</view>
    <block wx:for="{{techBackground}}" wx:key="title">
      <view class="about-item">
        <view class="row-between about-item-top">
          <view class="about-item-title">{{item.title}}</view>
          <view class="about-badge">{{item.badge}}</view>
        </view>
        <view class="about-copy about-item-desc">{{item.desc}}</view>
      </view>
    </block>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">问题反馈</view>
    <view class="about-copy">如果你在使用里遇到问题，或者希望我们补充新的能力，可以直接在这里提交，我们会按反馈继续优化。</view>
    <view class="about-field-card">
      <view class="about-label">提交反馈</view>
      <textarea class="textarea about-feedback-textarea" placeholder="例如：推荐结果哪里看不懂、哪块文案需要更直白，或某个页面使用时出现异常。" value="{{feedbackContent}}" bindinput="onFeedbackInput"></textarea>
      <button class="primary-btn" loading="{{feedbackSubmitting}}" bindtap="submitFeedback">告诉我们你的问题</button>
      <view class="about-copy" wx:if="{{feedbackSuccessMessage}}">{{feedbackSuccessMessage}}</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card about-card">
    <view class="section-title section-title-small">连接与诊断</view>
    <view class="about-copy">如果页面出现加载异常、网络报错或需要协助排查，可以在这里查看当前连接状态和最近一次诊断记录。</view>
    <view class="about-field-card">
      <view class="about-label">当前服务地址</view>
      <view class="about-static-value about-static-value-break">{{backendBaseUrl}}</view>
    </view>
    <view class="about-field-card">
      <view class="about-label">切换服务地址</view>
      <input class="input login-input" placeholder="例如：https://api.succ.online" value="{{backendBaseUrlInput}}" bindinput="onBackendBaseUrlInput" />
      <view class="about-copy">正常使用时建议保持默认地址。只有在排查网络问题时，才需要临时切换到其他地址。</view>
      <view class="about-preset-row">
        <button wx:for="{{backendPresets}}" wx:key="value" class="ghost-btn about-preset-btn" data-value="{{item.value}}" bindtap="useBackendPreset">{{item.label}}</button>
      </view>
      <button class="primary-btn" bindtap="applyBackendBaseUrl">切到这条线路</button>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="verifyBackendBaseUrl">帮我检测连接</button>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="resetBackendBaseUrl">恢复默认线路</button>
    </view>
    <view class="about-copy" wx:if="{{backendCheckMessage}}">{{backendCheckMessage}}</view>
    <view class="about-field-card">
      <view class="about-label">最近一次网络诊断</view>
      <view class="about-static-value about-static-value-break" wx:if="{{latestDiagnostic}}">{{latestDiagnostic.message}}</view>
      <view class="about-copy" wx:if="{{!latestDiagnostic}}">当前还没有保存的网络异常记录。</view>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="copyLatestDiagnostic" wx:if="{{latestDiagnostic}}">复制这条排查信息</button>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="openDiagnostics">查看完整排查记录</button>
      <button class="ghost-btn about-ghost-btn" bindtap="clearDiagnostics">清空诊断记录</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>